<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 100px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .btn-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #ffffff; /* Ensures the text is white */
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .btn-link:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            color: #ffffff; /* Keeps the text white on hover */
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #777777;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007BFF;
        }
        span{
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dil9kylo3/image/upload/v1723176952/erlgxgiyvgbfxmizkbfa.png" alt="Company Logo">
            <h2>{{subject}}</h2>
        </div>

        <hr/>

        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>

        <p>
            Thank you for creating an account with us. Please use the link below to verify your account. This link is valid for 24 hours.
        </p> 

        <a href="{{link}}" class="btn-link"><span>Verify Account</span></a>
        
        <p>If you didnâ€™t create an account, please ignore this email.</p>

        <hr/>

        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><strong>RangGo Team</strong></p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                If you're having trouble clicking the "Verify Account" button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:
                <br/>
                <a href="{{link}}">{{link}}</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
